{"tid":954751,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【教會冧閘】遭壓傷婦人情況嚴重 教會拒回應事件","createTime":"2018-12-24T22:58:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-25T16:42:55.000Z","uid":1188,"like":38,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"1d5df151946618719b343980dab08572fd91c82b","tid":954751,"uid":1188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T22:58:48.000Z","msg":"【教會冧閘】遭壓傷婦人情況嚴重 教會拒回應事件<br />\n<br />\n16小時前<br />\n<br />\n30.6K<br />\n即時突發<br />\n<br />\n64歲姓吳婦人昨晚到九龍城出席教會活動後，在教會門外等候丈夫之際，一扇至少數百磅的大閘突然鬆脫塌下，當場把她壓中，<span style=\"color: red;\">送院搶救後情況嚴重</span>。現場是嘉林邊道39號的基督教九龍城潮人生命堂，教會今早未見有人辦公，按門鐘無人應門，亦無教友出入，不過教會的大閘並沒有關閉，涉事鐵閘事後已被裝回，門柄位置掛上「請勿關閘」紙牌。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：教會塌大閘　壓傷六旬婦<br />\n<br />\n記者曾致電該教會，一女職員拒絕回應意外原因及會如何幫助女傷者，她只是強調已就塌鐵閘的問題作出適當處理。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7FBfmtH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7FBfmtH.png&h=ec47ad91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n女事主送院搶救後情況嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">又多一個耶撚準備上天堂同神相聚</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e66daf88a87dadc3cc3d017b0895e401b523111","tid":954751,"uid":191815,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T23:03:11.000Z","msg":"教會一定唔回應啦<br />\n應咗咪上身<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到時就屈死者推爛佢地道閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40d49dd3c17c46105728e58bbd9a379b6c52b89c","tid":954751,"uid":1188,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"7e66